2) The above mentioned promotion is being given in a purely temporary form subject to the following conditions.

1. Ma. The Special Leave Petition No. Subject to 28306/2017, all vacancies in the promotion quota shall be filled up. The approval is being given in accordance with the instructions of the Government Decision dated 7th May, 2021 of the Executive Board, S.P.V. / 16B regarding net provisional filling up as per the service superiority located at 25.5.2004. Also, vide Government Decision dated 7th May, 2021, Shri. The challenge has been filed in the High Court, Bombay and the promotion is being made subject to a final decision on the same.
The Government reserves the right to cancel the promotion granted to the said officers without any prior notice or intimation.

3) General Administration Department Notification. The "Maharashtra Civil Services (Regulation of Seniority) Rules, 2021" has been published under the 21/6/2021. All terms and conditions of this notification shall apply to all officers promoted by this order.

4) If the above promoted officers do not accept the net provisional promotion of the above mentioned post in the cadre of Sub-Divisional Water Conservation Officer (Construction) and other equivalent posts, the General Administration Department, Government Decision No. SRV No-2015 / Q303 / Ka-12D. Action will be taken under 12/9/2016.
5) This Government Order 777 of the Government of Maharashtra. 19. 1919511119.2009.11] is available on the website and their computer code is 202509191058545626.
6) These orders shall come into force with immediate effect, the promoted officer shall immediately join the post in which he is posted and submit a report thereon to the Government.
By order and in the name of the Governor of Maharashtra.
